EventBody:
Love is a complex emotion that has been the subject of philosophical, psychological, and artistic exploration for centuries. There is no single definition of love that is universally accepted, but it is generally understood to be a powerful emotion that involves feelings of intimacy, passion, and commitment.

* **Intimacy** refers to the feeling of closeness and connection that we have with another person. It involves sharing our deepest thoughts and feelings, and feeling comfortable being ourselves around them.
* **Passion** refers to the intense feelings of excitement, attraction, and desire that we have for another person. It can be expressed physically, emotionally, and intellectually.
* **Commitment** refers to the decision to stay with another person through thick and thin. It involves making a choice to prioritize your relationship with them, and to work through challenges together.

Love can be expressed in many different ways, and it can be experienced in different ways by different people. There are many different types of love, including romantic love, platonic love, familial love, and self-love.

Love can be a source of great joy and happiness, but it can also be a source of pain and sadness. When love is healthy, it can help us to feel connected, supported, and cherished. When love is unhealthy, it can lead to feelings of insecurity, jealousy, and control.

Ultimately, love is a mystery. It is something that we cannot fully explain or understand. But that doesn't mean that it is any less real or powerful. Love is a force that can shape our lives in profound ways, and it is something that we should all cherish.

𝗠𝗘𝗔𝗡𝗜𝗡𝗚𝗦
  ❑ noun
  ⌲ Strong affection.
  ⌲ A person who is the object of romantic feelings; a darling, a sweetheart, a beloved.
  ⌲ A term of friendly address, regardless of feelings.
  ⌲ A thing, activity etc which is the object of one's deep liking or enthusiasm.
  ⌲ Sexual desire; attachment based on sexual attraction.
  ⌲ Sexual activity.
  ⌲ An instance or episode of being in love; a love affair.
  ⌲ Used as the closing, before the signature, of a letter, especially between good friends or family members, or by the young.
  ⌲ Alternative letter-case form of Love.
  ⌲ A thin silk material.
  ⌲ A climbing plant, Clematis vitalba.

  ❑ verb
  ⌲ (usually transitive, sometimes intransitive, stative) To have a strong affection for (someone or something).
  ⌲ To need, thrive on.
  ⌲ To be strongly inclined towards something; an emphatic form of like.
  ⌲ (usually transitive, sometimes intransitive) To care deeply about, to be dedicated to (someone or something).
  ⌲ To derive delight from a fact or situation.
  ⌲ To have sex with (perhaps from make love).

𝗪𝗢𝗥𝗗: sliders

𝗠𝗘𝗔𝗡𝗜𝗡𝗚𝗦
  ❑ noun
  ⌲ An item of play equipment that children can climb up and then slide down again.
  ⌲ A surface of ice, snow, butter, etc. on which someone can slide for amusement or as a practical joke.
  ⌲ The falling of large amounts of rubble, earth and stones down the slope of a hill or mountain; avalanche.
  ⌲ An inclined plane on which heavy bodies slide by the force of gravity, especially one constructed on a mountainside for conveying logs by sliding them down.
  ⌲ A mechanism consisting of a part which slides on or against a guide.
  ⌲ The act of sliding; smooth, even passage or progress.
  ⌲ A lever that can be moved in two directions.
  ⌲ A valve that works by sliding, such as in a trombone.
  ⌲ A transparent plate bearing an image to be projected to a screen.
  ⌲ (by extension) A page of a computer presentation package such as PowerPoint.
  ⌲ A flat, usually rectangular piece of glass or similar material on which a prepared sample may be viewed through a microscope Generally referred to as a microscope slide.
  ⌲ The act of dropping down and skidding into a base
  ⌲ (guitar) A hand-held device made of smooth, hard material, used in the practice of slide guitar.
  ⌲ A lively dance from County Kerry, in 12/8 time.
  ⌲ A small dislocation in beds of rock along a line of fissure.
  ⌲ A grace consisting of two or more small notes moving by conjoint degrees, and leading to a principal note either above or below.
  ⌲ A sound which, by a gradual change in the position of the vocal organs, passes imperceptibly into another sound.
  ⌲ A clasp or brooch for a belt, etc.
  ⌲ (footwear) A shoe that is backless and open-toed.
  ⌲ (speech therapy) A voluntary stutter used as a technique to control stuttering in one's speech.

  ❑ noun
  ⌲ Agent noun of slide: one who slides.
  ⌲ A sliding door.
  ⌲ A pitch thrown with added pressure by middle and ring fingers yielding a combination of backspin and sidespin, resulting in a motion to the left when thrown by a right handed pitcher.
  ⌲ A similar delivery in which the wrist and ring finger work to impart backspin to the ball.
  ⌲ A small hamburger.
  ⌲ A piece of Teflon or similar material attached to a curling shoe that allows the player to slide along the ice.
  ⌲ The movable part of a zip fastener that opens or closes the row of teeth.
  ⌲ A widget allowing the user to select a value or position on a sliding scale.
  ⌲ A slideshow on a web page.
  ⌲ The red-bellied terrapin (Pseudemys rubriventris, syn. Pseudemys rugosa).
  ⌲ (skydiving) A rectangle of fabric that helps produce an orderly parachute deployment.
  ⌲ An open-toed and backless sandal

EventBody:
Vice versa is a Latin phrase used to indicate that the opposite of a previous statement is also true. In mathematics, an example of vice versa can be seen in the statement "If a quadrilateral is a square, then it is a rectangle." This means that if a shape is a square, it will also have the properties of a rectangle, such as having four right angles. Vice versa, the statement "If a quadrilateral is a rectangle, then it is a square" is also true, meaning that if a shape is a rectangle, it will also have the properties of a square, such as having all sides equal in length.

EventBody:
Magandang hapon sa inyong lahat!

Sa pagkakataong ito, nais kong ibahagi sa inyo ang isang mahalagang usapin na ating kinakaharap bilang isang bansa. 

Tayo ay nasa gitna ng isang krisis sa ating kalikasan. Hindi na natin maitatanggi ang patuloy na pagbabago ng klima, ang patuloy na pagkawala ng mga puno at halaman, ang patuloy na pagkasira ng ating mga karagatan at kabundukan.

Ang ating kalikasan ay isa sa ating pinakamahalaga at pinakasustenidong yaman. Hindi ito lamang nagbibigay sa atin ng malinis na hangin at tubig, kundi pati na rin ng mga lokal at global na serbisyo sa ekolohiya. Subalit, sa halos lahat ng dako ng mundo, tinataya na ang ating kalikasan ay papunta na sa punto ng kawalan.

Ang pagbabago ng klima ay isa sa mga pinakamalaking hamon na ating kinakaharap ngayon. Dumarami ang mga malalalang bagyo, matinding tag-init at taglamig, at malalawak na tagtuyot. Ito ay nagdudulot ng pinsala sa ating mga tanim at pag-aani, at nagiging sanhi ng kagutuman sa iba't ibang pook ng ating bansa.

Ang pagkasira ng ating mga kabundukan at karagatan ay isa rin sa mga alalahanin natin. Ito ay nagdudulot ng baha, pagguho ng lupa, at pagsira ng mga kritikal na tahanan ng iba't ibang uri ng halaman at hayop. Ang pagkawala ng mga puno at halaman ay nagiging dahilan din ng pagtaas ng mga sakit na dala ng polusyon, gaya ng hika at iba pang respiratoryo.

Ngunit, hindi pa huli ang lahat. Tayo mismo ang makakagawa ng pagbabago sa ating kalikasan.

Una, mahalagang magsimula tayo sa ating sarili. Maging responsable tayo sa ating paggamit ng enerhiya at mga likas na yaman. Matutong magbawas ng paggamit ng kuryente at tubig. Piliin nating maglakad o gumamit ng bisikleta sa halip na gamitin ang sasakyan. 

Pangalawa, kailangan nating ipaalam sa iba ang kahalagahan ng pangangalaga sa kalikasan. Edukasyon at pagbibigay impormasyon sa ating mga kapwa Pilipino ang magiging susi upang mapaunlad ang pag-unlad ng sariwang kapaligiran. 

Panghuli, kilalanin natin ang mga organisasyon at grupo na aktibong nagtatanggol at nagpapalaganap ng pangangalaga sa kalikasan. Sumama tayo sa mga environmental clean-up drives o mga tree planting activities. Mag-volunteer tayo sa mga gawaing may kinalaman sa pagpapanatili ng kalinisan ng mga ilog, dagat, at kagubatan.

Napakahalaga ang papel natin sa pangangalaga sa kalikasan. Sa ating mga kamay nakasalalay ang kinabukasan ng ating mga anak at ng susunod pang henerasyon. 

Kaya't sa mga darating na araw, sana'y ating isaisip at isakatuparan ang mga hakbang na ating napag-usapan upang mapanatiling malinis at maayos ang ating kalikasan. Tandaan natin na ang pag-aalaga sa kalikasan ay hindi lamang para sa atin, kundi para sa lahat ng buhay sa mundong ito.

Sa ating sama-sama at patuloy na pagtutulungan, sigurado akong kayang-kaya nating solusyunan ang mga suliraning ito.

Maraming salamat sa inyong pakikinig, at hinihiling kong patuloy tayong magsikap at magkaisa upang protektahan at alagaan ang ating kalikasan.

Mabuhay ang Pilipinas!
